 22. A3-li7-kan2 sou2 Bang7-kiN3 
 U7 lang5 liah8 ka-ki7 choe3 ho2 lang5 lai5 khoaN3-khin pat8-lang5. Ia5-sou chiong phi3-ju7 ka3-si7 in. Che phi3-ju7 e5 oe7 ki3-chai3 ti7 Lou7-ka 18:9. 
 Cha2 u7 hit ho7 chu7-chheng choe3 ho2 e5 lang5, hian7-si5 iah8 u7. Hit ho7 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 toa7-toa7 ka-ki7 phian3. 
 Ti7 bou2 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 Hoe5-hoe5 kau3 e5 lang5 mia5 kio3 A3-li7-kan2. Chiau3 lang5 khoaN3 si7 put-chi2 the2-bian7, koh si7 jiat8-sim hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 i siong5-siong5 chin gau5 ki5-to2, kim3-chiah8, chin2-che3 song3-hiong lang5. Chong2-si7 i kiaN5 an2-ni tiau5-kou3-i3 beh hou7 lang5 khoaN3, tui3 lang5 kiu5 eng5-kng; m7-si7 seng5-sit8 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3, si7 oa2-kho3 ka-ki7 e5 ho2, oh8 Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 ki5-to2 kong2, ¡§Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 goa2 m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 pat8-lang5.¡¨ 
 U7 chit8-jit8 i teh kiaN5-lou7 e5 si5, u7 tu2-tioh8 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2. Hit e5 peng5-iu2 khoaN3-kiN3 A3-li7-kan2 u7 iu-thau5 khou2-bin7 chiu7 liah8 choe3 ki5-koai3, in-ui7 i peng5-si5 liah8 ka-ki7 si7 ho2 m7-bat u7 iu-bun7 e5 bin7-sek. TaN khoaN3 i an2-ni chiu7 mng7 i kong2, ¡§A3-li7-kan2--ah, li2 teh iu-bun7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 ? Si7 lin2 ke-lai7 u7 lang5 phoa3-piN7 mah ? A2-si7 seng-li2 choe3 liau2 sih8-pun2 mah ?¡¨ 
 A3-li7-kan2 in3 kong2, ¡§Bo5, goan2 tau bo5 lang5 piN7, seng-li2 iah8 bo5 sih8-pun2, tok8-tok8 cha7-mi5 goa2 u7 bang7-kiN3 chit8 e5 bang7,hou7 goa2 put-chi2 kiaN sim-lai7 chin kan-khou2. Chit-tiap8 goa2 beh khi3 Su-li7-ma2 chiu7-si7 goan2 peh in tau, i si7 toa7 phok-hak8 e5 lang5 liong7-siong2 oe7 ka7 goa2 oan5 hit e5 bang7.¡¨ 
 Hit e5 peng5-iu2 ki-chhi3 ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 m7-thang khi3 mng7 Su-li7-ma2 i kun7-lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou thak8 Seng3-chheh, i oe7 phah-phian3 li2, ka-ki7 khoaN3 bo5 lou7 thai2-thou2 oe7 chhoa7 pat8-lang5. ¡¨ 
 A3-li7-kan2 kong2, ¡§KaN2 m7 si7 an2-ni mah ? I i2-keng kui2-na7 pai2 bat eng7 ti3-sek e5 oe7 chi2-si7 goa2, sou2-i2 chit-tiap8 beh koh khi3 chheng2-kau3 i.¡¨ 
 Kong2 soah sui5-si5 chiu7 khi3 Su-li7-ma2 in tau kap i kiaN5 le2, saN-kap che7-loh8 kong2 khi2, i sou2 bang7-kiN3 e5 tai7-chi3 hou7 in peh thiaN, kong2, ¡§Goa2 bang7-kiN3 goa2 i2-keng ke3-ong2, sin-si hou7 lang5 tai5, leng5-hun5 bo5 si2 iau2 ti7-teh. Koh bang7-kiN3 chit8-ki toa7 thian-peng5 si7 kim e5, thian-peng5 thiau7 koaiN5 kau3 tu2 thiN. Goa2 khia7 ti7 hia u7 sin5 beh lai5 pheng5 goa2 it-seng sou2 kiaN5 e5 ho2 phaiN2. Ho2 e5 beh he7 ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 pheng5-oaN2, phaiN2 e5 he7 ti7 to3 peng5 e5 pheng5-oaN2. Na7 si7 ho2 e5 khah tang7 chiu7 thiN-sai3 beh hu5 goa2 khi3 thian-tong5, na7-si7 phaiN2 e5 khah tang7 chiu7 Mou5-kui2 beh thoa goa2 kau3 te7-gek8. Koh khoaN3-kiN3 Mou5-kui2 e5 bin7 chin hiong5 chin phaiN2 khoaN3, bak8-chiu kim na3-na3 chhin-chhiuN7 toh8 he2 e5 thou5-thoaN3.¡¨ 
 In peh Su-li2-ma2 in3 kong2, ¡§Li2 khoaN3-kiN3 kau3 an2-ni kaN2 oe7 hou7 li2 kiaN kau3 kheh8-kheh8 tio7 houN3 ?¡¨ 
 A3-li7-kan2 in3 kong2, ¡§Khi2-thau5 bo5 kau3 joa7 toa7 kiaN ka-ki7 siuN7 peng5-si5 e5 sou2 kiaN5 bo5 sim2-mih8 toa7 m7 tioh8, thong siaN5 e5 lang5 bo5 lang5 oe7 tat8-tit goa2 hiah keng3-khian5, gau5 siu2 kai3-lut8. Ka-ki7 siuN7 bo5 sim2-mih8 phaiN2-tai7 thang he7 ti7 to3-peng5 e5 pheng5-oaN2, sou2-i2 hit-tiap8 goa2 chiah bo5 kiaN, jian5-au7 oat8 thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit tin7 ou-ou chin beng2 e5 kui2 tak8-e5 kim-kim siong3 goa2, chiah chai kiaN.¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 koh mng7 kong2, ¡§Iau2 u7 bang7-kiN3 pat8 mih8 bo5 ?¡¨ 
 In3 kong2, U7--ah koh bang7-kiN3 chit8 tin7 ou e5 kui2 kiaN5-oa2 kau3 thian-peng5 tak8 e5 teh taN chit8 taN3 chin tang7 e5 ou mih8. Hiah-e5 ou mih8 chiu7 si7 goa2 tiam3 se3-kan e5 si5 sou2 kiaN5 e5 choe7-koa3. Goa2 teh khoaN3 e5 si5 u7 saN hang7 hou7 goa2 chin ki5-koai3, chiu7-si7 ki5-koai3 chiah-e5 ou-mih8 kau3 chiah choe7, kau3 chiah toa7, iah8 kau3 chiah tang7. Goa2 sou2 liah8 choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2 e5 su7 taN khoaN3 si7 chin tang7 e5 choe7. Kui2 tak8 e5 kau3 chiu7 piaN3 i sou2 taN e5 ti7 to3-peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. Hit peng5-oaN2 liam5-piN tui7-loh8 kau3 chin ke7. 
 Sat-tan3 chiu7 oat8 thau5 siong3 goa2, siuN7 tek-khak beh liah8 goa2. Sat-tan3 chiu7 koh hoan-hu3 chit tin7 phaiN2 kui2 kong2, ¡§A3-li7-kan2 sou2 bat kong2 e5 phaiN2-oe7 tioh8 taN lai5.¡¨ Goa2 hit-si5 sit8-chai7 gong7-ngiah8, long2 bo5 phah-sng3 goa2 bat kong2 kau3 hiah choe7 phaiN2 oe7. U7 si5 bat hoat siu7-khi3 kong2 chhut phaiN2 oe7 chong2-si7 bo5 liah8 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 su7. Hit ho7 e5 phaiN2-oe7 chhin-chhiuN7 ou e5 cheng2-chi2, u7 e5 toa7 liap8, u7 e5 soe3 liap8, tak8 liap8 chin tang7. Chin choe7 kui2 teh taN lai5, tak8 e5 ki-chhi3 goa2, kiaN5 chin3-cheng5 piaN3 in sou2 taN e5 phaiN2-oe7 ti7 to3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. Goa2 chiu7 ki3-tit siok8-gu2 kong2, ¡§Kha poah8-to2 oe7 peh khi2 lai5, chhui3 kong2 chhut boe7 koh siu to3-tng2.¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Ia5-sou e5 oe7 pi2 siok8-gu2 si7 koh khah ho2. I bat kong2, Goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2, kong2 oe7 lam7-sam2 tek-khak ti7 siu7 sim2-phoaN3 e5 jit8 hou7 Siong7-te3 sim2-phoaN3, in-ui7 chiau3 li2 e5 oe7 chiu7 chheng-gi7, iah8 chiau3 li2 e5 oe7 chiu7 gi2-choe7.¡¨(Ma2-thai3 12 :36, 37) 
 A3-li7-kan2 thou2-khui3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 kaN2 u7 bat kong2 chit8 ban7 ku3 phaiN2 oe7 long2 boe7 sng3-tit. To3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2 tang7 kau3 beh loh8 te7-gek8. Ai-ah ! kau3 an2-ni iau2-be7 liau2,iau2 u7 khah chham2 e5 su7, chiu7-si7 hit si5 Sat-tan3 koh toa7-siaN hoan-hu3 kong2, ¡§A3-li7-kan2 phaiN2 e5 liam7-thau5 tioh8 taN lai5 !¡¨ ThiaN chit8 ku3 goa2 koh thou2-khui3 kong2, ¡§Ai-ah ! liam7-thau5 iah8 tioh8 siu7 kam3-chhat mah ?¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 in3-kong2, ¡§Seng3-chheh u7 ki3-chai3, phaiN2 e5 liam7-thau5 si7 tui3 sim khi2, che si7 bak la5-sam5 lang5.¡¨ (Ma2-thai3 15:19,20 ) 
 A3-li7-kan2 kong2, Kui2 sui5-si5 taN lai5, Chiah-e5 phaiN2 e5 liam7-thau5 chiau3 bak8-chiu khoaN3 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 ou-ian, Chong2-si7 toa7-toa7 bo5 tang5, in-ui7 ou-ian si7 khin-khin, phaiN2 e5 liam7-thau5 chin chiaN3 tang7, Kui2 piaN3 ti7 to3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2, hou7 hit oaN2 loh8 koh khah ke7 kau3 jip8 chit8 e5 chhim-ian, Chhim-ian thou3-chhut he2 chih8 kap ou hun. Hit si5 goa2 hiam2-hiam2 sit-bang7, hut-jian5 ki3-tit goa2 sou2 kiaN5 e5 ho2 u7 iau2-be7 hou7 i pheng5. Goa2 siuN7 ho2 su7 un2-tang3 choe7-choe7, chiu7 toa7-siaN kio3 thiN-sai3 kong2, Ho2 tioh8 kin2-kin2 taN lai5 ! Goa2 sou2 bat chin2-che3 lang5, sou2 bat kim3-chiah8, chiah-e5 ho2 su7 tioh8 kin2-me2 piaN3 ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. Goa2 siuN7 chit-tiap8 chiaN3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2 tek-khak pi2 to3 peng5 e5 khah tang7, hou7 to3 peng5 koaiN5-koaiN5 chiaN3 peng5 ke7-ke7. 
 ThiN-sai3 kui2 na7 e5 ban7-ban7 lai5, tak8 e5 teh taN chit8 taN3 peh8 e5 mih8. Thau5-cheng5 e5 thiN-sai3 khui chhui3 kong2, ¡§Lang5 kiaN5 ho2-su7 in-ui7 ai3 kui eng5-kng Siong7-te3, hit ho7 su7 sng3 si7 tang7, na7 kiaN5 ho2 su7 ai3 tit choe3 kong-lo5, hit ho7 su7 chiu7 sng3 si7 khin chhin-chhiuN7 chiau2-mng5. Li2 it-seng sou2 kiaN5 e5 ho2-su7 goan2 taN-liau2 si7 khin-khin.¡¨ 
 Kong2-soah thiN-sai3 tak8 e5 piaN3 in sou2 taN e5 peh8 mih8 ti7 chiaN3 peng5 oaN2. Hiah-e5 mih8 sit8-chai7 khin, thian-peng5 long2 bo5 chit8 tiam2-a2 tin2-tang7. Khou2 ah ! Goa2 sou2 kim3-chiah8 kap chin2-che3 lang5, chiah-e5 su7 long2 kui ti7 bo5. 
 Koh siuN7, goa2 peng5-si5 ki5-to2 hit chat su7 iau2-be7 taN lai5 pheng5, chiu7 kiu5-kio3 thiN-sai3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 ki5-to2 e5 su7 ! Goa2 ki5-to2 e5 su7 ! Tioh8 kin2-kin2 taN lai5. Goa2 chit8 jit8 ki5-to2 u7 gou7 pai2, i2-keng ki5-to2 chiah choe7 ni5, an2-ni chiah-e5 ki5-to2 e5 su7 tek-khak ke3-thau5 tang7.¡¨ Goa2 tui3 thiN-sai3 kong2-liau2 hit-si5 hou7 goa2 toa7 ki5-koai3, boe7 beng5-pek8, in-ui7 khoaN3-kiN3 hiah-e5 thiN-sai3 chiong goa2 peh8-peh8 e5 ki5-to2 kau hou7 ou kui2. Hiah-e5 ou kui2 chit8 e7 chhut chhiu2 lai5 beh taN; bong-liau2 peh8-e5 liam5-piN piN3 choe3 ou, chiu7 taN khi3 piaN3-loh8 to3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2.¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 kong2, ¡§Hit-e5 cheng5-heng5 chaiN2-iuN7 an2-ni, goa2 beh ka7 li2 kong2, tek-khak si7 tui3 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 bo5 seng5-sit8, bo5 keng3-khian5. Chhui3 ki5-to2, sim siat-tok8, goa7-phe5 keng3-ui3, lai7-sim kiau-ngou7, chiu7-si7 phah la5-sam5 Siong7-te3 seng3-mia5, chhin-chhiuN7 hoan7 tioh8 te7 saN tiau5 seng3 e5 kai3-beng7, sou2-i2 boe7 sng3-tit si7 ho2, hoan2-tng2 sng3 si7 phaiN2. ThiN-sai3 chiah bo5 lai5 ka7 li2 taN, tok8-tok8 u7 kio3 hiah-e5 ou-kui2 lai5 ka7 li2 taN, hou7 li2 chai li2 it-seng ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 boe7 sng3-tit si7 ho2.A3-li7-kan2 ah, li2 u7 koh bang7-kiN3 sim2-mih8 ?¡¨ 
 In3 kong2, ¡§U7, bang7-kiN3 phaiN2 kui2 lai5 liah8 goa2, hit-si5 kiaN kau3 cheng-sin5. Peh-ah, m7 chai bat thiaN-kiN3 lang5 bang7-kiN3 phaiN2 bang7 kau3 an2-ni bo5 ?¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 in3 kong2, ¡§Cheng-sin5 e5 si5, goa2 bat siuN7 chit ho7 e5 to7-li2, bat khoaN3 goa2 sou2 kiaN5 sou2 siuN7 long2-chong2 hou7 Siong7-te3 sim2-phoaN3. U7 chit8 chat Seng3-chheh hou7 goa2 kiaN kau3 ngiauh8-ngiauh8-chhoah, chiu7-si7 kong2 ¡¥Siong7-te3 pheng5 li2, chai li2 u7 khiam3-kheh,¡¦ (Tan7. 5: 27. ) Goa2 long2 bo5 chit8 chat ho2 su7 thang lok ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. A3-li7-kan2 ah, goa2 siuN7 an2-ni chiu7 kiu5-kio3 kong2, ¡¥Siong7-te3 ah, tioh8 lin5-bin2 goa2 u7 choe7 e5 lang5 !¡¨ 
 A3-li7-kan2 mng7 kong2, ¡§An2-ni se3-kan lang5 long2 bo5 thang ng3-bang7 mah ? Kiam2 bo5 sim2-mih8 tang7 e5 mih8 thang lok ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 oaN2, hou7 to3 peng5 oe7 khah khin m7 sai2 loh8 te7-gek8 ?¡¨ 
 Su-li7-ma2 in3 kong2, ¡§Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 ! Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 ! M7 sai2 sit-bang7, goa2 bat khoaN3-kiN3 Ia5-sou e5 po2 huih chit8 tiam2 tih ti7 chiaN3 peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. Chit8 tiam2 pi2 to3-peng5-oaN2 sou2 toe2 e5 phaiN2 khah tang7. To3-peng5 liam5-piN khi2 chin koaiN5. Goa2 e5 choe7 long2 bo5 khi3, eng2-eng2 bo5 khi3, boe7 koh chai3 khoaN3-kiN3. Sim toa7 hoaN-hi2 kio3 kong2, Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 huih soe2-tu5 long2-chong2 e5 choe7.¡¨ 
 A3-li7-kan2 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Su7-li7-ma2 ah, li2 kaN2 si7 choe3 Ia5-sou e5 hak8-seng ?¡¨ 
 In3 kong2, ¡§Si7 ah, Seng3-chheh kap liong5-sim chim-chiok ka3-si7 goa2, hou7 goa2 chai lang5 e5 choe7 si7 chin tang7, na7 bo5 Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5 thang he7 ti7 chiaN3-peng5 e5 thian-peng5-oaN2. Lang5 chiu7 bo5 thang ng3-bang7.¡¨ 
 23. Kim Ham-leng5 kap Siah8-liu5 
 U7 chit8 chat Seng3-chheh kong2, ¡§Ti7 che3-si-thau5 kong-hok8 e5 e7-kha-pou5 tioh8 eng7 kim ham-leng5 kap siah8-liu5 lai5 saN-kaiN3.¡¨ Chit chat hong2-hut khoaN3 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5 sim2-mih8 thang gi7-lun7, Chong2-si7 na7 siong5-se3 siuN7 chiu7 put-chi2 u7 to7-li2 thang ka3-si7. U7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 eng7 chit8 chat e5 oe7 tiau3 ti7 lang5-kheh thiaN e5 mng5 bai5 teng2. U7 lang5 mng7 i kong2, ¡§Seng3-chheh lai7 kiam2 bo5 pat8 e5 chiuN-chat pi2 chit chat khah beng5, iah8 khah u7 ka3-si7 ? SiaN2-su7 tiau3 chit chat ti7 li2 e5 mng5 bai5 teng2 ?¡¨ I in3 kong2, ¡§U7 iaN2, goa2 iau2 u7 pat8 e5 chiuN-chat put-chi2 khah beng5, iah8 put-chi2 khah sui2. U7 e5 si7 kim e5 u7 e5 si7 ngou2-sek e5 , na7-si7 chit e5 ji7 sui-bong2 khiap si3, sia2 iah8 bo5 tit, iau2-ku2 goa2 teh bong ke-lai7 e5 tai7-chi3 e5 si5, na7 giah8 thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit chat, chiu7 hou7 goa2 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 I u7 eng7 chit chat hou7 goa2 e5 sim siu7 kam2-kek. 
 TaN goa2 beh lioh8-a2 kong2 khi2 hit e5 tai7-chi3. Goa2 si7 chiu2-koaN2 lang5, u7 khui chit8 keng tiam3, iah8 u7 kiaN2-ji5, sou2-i2 thong le2-pai3 e5 lai7-bin7 tioh8 chhut-lat8 choe3 kang, chiah u7 thang tou7-pa2, tui3 an2-ni goa2 e5 sim siong5-siong5 hun-loan7, Chong2-si7 kau3 Le2-pai3-jit8 goa2 chiu7 koaiN-tiam3, pang3-soah chiah-e5 se3-su7 khi3 le2-pai3, ka-ki7 phah-sng3 goa2 e5 jiat8-sim bat to7-li2 iaN5 ke3 choe7-choe7 lang5. U7 chit8 e5 Le2-pai3 e5-hng goa2 iu5-goan5 khi3 le2-pai3 , hit e5 kong2 to7-li2 e5 sian-siN m7 si7 goan2 e5 bok8-su, chiu7-si7 siN-hun7 lang5. I sou2 kong2 e5 toe5-bak8 chiu7-si7 Chhut Ai-kip8 ki3 39 chiuN 26 chat, chiu7-si7 kong2, ¡§Ti7 che3-si-thau5 kong-hok8 e5 e7-kha-pou5 tioh8 eng7 kim ham-leng5 kap siah8-liu5 lai5 saN-kaiN3.¡¨ Goa2 thiaN liau2 chiu7 siuN7 kong2, chit-tiap8 si7 hok-im e5 se3-tai7, siaN2-su7 koh chai3 kong2 khi2 Iu5-thai3 lang5 Ku7-iok e5 le2-sou3 ? Goa2 chiu7 che7 teh bong2 thiaN, phah-sng3 chit chat bo5 sim2-mih8 thang ka3-si7 goa2, choe3 goa2 siuN7 tang, siuN7 sai. 
 Au7-lai5 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2, Goa2 iah8 tioh8 thiaN thang choe3 pat8 lang5 e5 iuN7, chiu7 thiaN-kiN3 bok8-su teh kong2, ¡§Lin2 si7 seng3 e5 che3-si, oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3, hoaN-hi2 kam3-lap8 leng5 e5 che3-su7.¡¨ Au7-lai5 i chiu7 kong2, ¡¥Lan2 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 m7-na7 tioh8 u7 mia5 iah8 tioh8 u7 sit8, chhin-chhiuN7 che3-si-thau5 e5 kong-hok8 m7-na7 u7 ho2 thiaN e5 ham-leng5, iah8 u7 chin tiN e5 ke2-chi2.¡¨ Goa2 thiaN kau3 chit ku3 goa2 e5 sim iau2 peng5-an, in-ui7 goa2 siuN7 goa2 e5 pai3 Siong7-te3 cheng3-lang5 long2 chai, goa2 bo5 khng3-bat8, an2-ni goa2 si7 u7 ham-leng5, Chong2-si7 au7-lai5 thiaN-kiN3 i koh gi7-lun7 e5, goa2 e5 sim chiu7 tam7-poh8 kan-khou2. I kong2, ¡§Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 iah8 u7 ham-leng5 choe7-choe7, chhin-chhiuN7 ki5-to2, kim3-chiah8, chin2-che3, oe7 chhut siaN e5 ham-leng5, Chong2-si7 chiah-e5 ham-leng5 m7 si7 kim e5, in e5 siaN chin phaiN2 thiaN; lang5 chha-put-to ai3 ng in e5 hi7-khang, m7-na7 phaiN2 thiaN na7-tiaN7, iah8 si7 long2 bo5 ke2-chi2, chiu7-si7 bo5 jin5-ai3, bo5 chu5-pi, bo5 sun7-hok8 Siong7-te3. Pi2-tek iah8 u7 ham-leng5, i e5 ham-leng5, bat chhut siaN kong2, ¡§Goa2 sui-bong2 kap Li2 si2, iah8 m7 kong2 m7-bat Li2.¡¨ Chong2-si7 kau3 au7-lai5 khoaN3 ke2-chi2 ti7 tah8-loh8 ? Ni5-ko-ti2-bo2 khiok u7 tam7-poh8 e5 ke2-chi2, chong2-si7 long2 bo5 ham-leng5, in-ui7 i m7-kaN2 jit8-si5 lai5 chiu7-kun7 Ia5-sou. 
 Iau2-ku2 au7-lai5 i iah8 u7, chiu7-si7 pian7-pok kong-hoe7 kong2, ¡§Be7 thiaN Ia5-sou e5 hun-sou3 liam5-piN teng7 i e5 choe7, kiam2 si7 chiau3 lut8-hoat ?¡¨ Koh Kiu3-chu2 si2 e5 si5 i kap A-li7-ma2-thai3 e5 Iok-sek chhut thau5 lai5 bai5-chong3 Kiu3-chu2. An2-ni u7 ke2-chi2 iah8 u7 ham-leng5. 
